211
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:26,700
Let me go! You're hurting me.
放开我 你弄疼我了

212
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,140
Am I gonna die?
我要死了吗

213
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:37,980
No. You just need some sleep.
你只是会多睡会儿

214
00:21:38,260 --> 00:21:39,740
I may vomit.
我想吐

215
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:45,620
This is just like<i> Love's Savage Secret</i>.
这就像 <i>《爱的残酷秘密》</i>

216
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:56,140
