Freeze! Put your weapon on the ground!
不许动 放下枪

223
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:25,620
Put your weapon on the ground now!
把枪放在地上

224
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:29,700
Right now!
快

225
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:36,980
So you're saying this was CIA sanctioned?
这么说 这是中情局内部制裁

226
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:40,100
All right, Thelma, thanks. I owe you one. Bye.
好的 希尔玛 谢谢 欠你个人情

227
00:23:55,420 --> 00:23:57,140
So it's like that, huh?
结束了吗

228
00:23:57,500 --> 00:24:00,300
Yeah. It's like that.
没错 你完了

229
00:24:11,940 --> 00:24:13,460
Where are we?
我们在哪儿

230
