Wow, I really hate you right now.
现在我恨透你了

232
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:28,380
I was just hoping you'd be a little more understanding of the situation.
我只是希望你能 多明白一点 现在的状况

233
00:24:28,460 --> 00:24:32,420
I was hoping not to get kidnapped. Or drugged.
我只是希望别被绑架 或下药

234
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:34,860
I was hoping you'd have hair.
我希望你有头发

235
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:38,660
So it looks like none of our dreams are coming true, at the moment.
貌似迄今为止 我设想的美梦 一个都没实现

236
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:40,140
Sorry about that.
不好意思

237
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:45,220
Thanks for saving me. I guess.
谢谢你救了我

238
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:48,660
No problem.
没关系

239
00:24:48,740 --> 00:24:51,820
Not my best first date.
不算最好的约会

240
