She used to live in Chinatown.
生前住在唐人街

246
00:25:24,340 --> 00:25:28,660
Okay. Here we go. Let's come in here. Right here. Wait a second.
这边走 进去 就这儿 等一下

247
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:31,100
You just hang onto this tape.
帮我拿着胶带

248
00:25:31,260 --> 00:25:32,940
No, you said we were just gonna talk to her.
你不是说我们只跟她谈谈话吗

249
00:25:33,020 --> 00:25:34,740
We are. This'll help.
是啊 这个有用

250
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:37,380
The woman just lost her daughter.
人家女儿 刚刚被害了

251
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:39,620
You can't just go around duct taping everyone.
你不能总是走进去用胶带绑人

252
00:25:39,940 --> 00:25:43,220
People are basically kind of decent.
大家都是正经人

253
00:25:44,860 --> 00:25:46,780
That hasn't always been my experience.
我的生活里 这个不常见

254
00:25:50,140 --> 00:25:51,780
Let me try and talk to her.
让我试着和她谈

255
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:54,740
-What? -Just let me do it.
-什么 -就让我去说

256
00:25:58,740 --> 00:26:00,300
They told me to be patient.
他们告诉我耐心点

257
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:03,300
The police have done nothing.
警方什么也不干

258
00:26:03,460 --> 00:26:08,300
They said it was just a burglary, but nothing was missing.
他们说是入室盗窃 但东西一样都没丢

259
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:10,140
She was scared.
她被害了

260
00:26:11,300 --> 00:26:13,300
We're hoping we can do more.
我们希望能多做点

261
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:17,100
You worked with my Stephanie?
你是斯丹芬妮同事吗

262
00:26:26,340 --> 00:26:28,020
She sent me this.
她给我寄了这个

263
00:26:29,380 --> 00:26:31,660
I got it in the mail on the day she died.
她死那天我收到的

264
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:40,340
What does this mean?
这是什么意思

265
00:26:40,660 --> 00:26:41,820
I don't know.
我不知道

266
00:26:42,020 --> 00:26:43,660
I tried dialing the numbers.
我拨了上面的号码

267
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:46,100
Police had no idea.
警察也没头绪

268
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,860
Where did Stephanie go to college?
斯丹芬妮在哪儿上的大学

269
00:26:52,420 --> 00:26:53,700
Why are we here again?
我们现在去哪儿

270
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,940
Those numbers on Stephanie Chan's postcard
斯丹芬妮•陈 明信片上的数字

271
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:57,860
are actually a call number for a book.
是书的条形码

272
00:26:57,940 --> 00:26:59,540
Call numbers start with letters.
以字母开头的数字

273
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,860
In the Library of Congress, yeah.
国会图书馆

274
00:27:02,020 --> 00:27:05,620
In Harvard-Yenching, it's a classification for Asian literature.
在 哈佛-燕京 亚洲文学类

275
00:27:06,540 --> 00:27:08,180
How could you possibly know that?
你怎么知道这些的

276
00:27:08,260 --> 00:27:10,300
几年前 我住在 武汉

277
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:14,540
You speak Chinese?
你会讲汉语

278
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:39,300
Unbelievable.
不可思议

279
00:27:42,420 --> 00:27:45,420
Hank Maestriano died 2 weeks ago. Car crash.
汉克•马斯特尼奥 两周前身故 车祸

280
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:49,740
Daniel McGinty. Heart attack. Last week.
丹尼尔•麦克金帝 心脏病 上周

281
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:56,700
But if this is a hit list, why is this guy still alive? Gabriel Singer.
但如果这就是打击名单 为什么这家伙还活着 加布里尔•辛格

282
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,940
Flies cargo planes.
运输机驾驶员

283
00:28:02,620 --> 00:28:04,300
That's a good question.
问得好

284
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:16,780
Hell of a mess.
一团糟啊

285
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:18,580
Come on.
快接呀

286
00:28:28,740 --> 00:28:30,220
Joe Matheson, please.
请接 乔•马希森

287
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:32,940
Hold on.
等一下

288
00:28:36,620 --> 00:28:37,620
Marna.
玛娜

289
00:28:38,980 --> 00:28:40,220
Hello?
你是

290
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:01,820
What?
怎么了

291
00:29:09,300 --> 00:29:10,300
Joe.
乔死了

292
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:20,500
Frank Moses is not a retired analyst who's never worked in the field.
弗兰克•摩西 可不是什么退休分析员 从没上过一线

293
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,980
This guy has a history.
这家伙深藏不露

294
00:29:43,700 --> 00:29:45,020
That's a file number.
这是档案编号

295
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:47,940
You need to visit the back room.
你去地下室查一下

296
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:50,500
You're going to meet the Records Keeper.
拜会一下档案管理员

297
00:29:58,820 --> 00:30:01,140
I didn't even know this place existed.
我甚至都不知道存在这种地方

298
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:03,060
It doesn't.
的确不存在

299
00:30:17,660 --> 00:30:19,380
Frank Moses' file.
弗兰克•摩西的档案

300
00:30:31,420 --> 00:30:33,420
You gotta be kidding me.
这事开玩笑吧

301
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:38,060
Frank Moses was one of the most effective black op agents we've ever had.
弗兰克•摩西 是迄今我们最优秀的特工之一

302
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:43,500
He retired drug-lords, terrorists. Hell, he toppled governments.
他抓过毒贩、恐怖分子 甚至扳倒过政府

303
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:48,900
He was truly gifted.
他真是天赋异秉

304
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:51,220
Why was he retired?
他因何退休

305
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:52,580
He got old.
老了

306
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:56,820
Then some thumb-sucker came along and tagged him "RED."
后来一些大佬过来 给他标记为“RED”

307
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:57,860
Red?
红色

308
00:30:57,940 --> 00:31:01,940
Yeah. RED. R-E-D. "Retired: Extremely Dangerous."
是 红色 R-E-D：退休、极端 危险

309
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:07,620
They don't make them like that anymore.
就这样把档案全毁了

310
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,620
Thanks.
谢谢

311
00:31:13,180 --> 00:31:14,220
I'm gonna need a data haunt.
我要一个数据师

312
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:16,820
Every flake he was ever involved in. Every agent he's ever run.
他涉及的所有资料 参与的每个项目

313
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,780
I want NSA telephone surveillance, voice recognition...
我要国安局的电话监控 声音识别

314
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:26,980
We have to find Marvin Boggs.
我们必须找到 马文•博格斯

315
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:29,380
Marvin died two years ago in a fire.
马文两年前火灾去世了

316
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:32,380
Marvin has died many times.
马文死了好多次了

317
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:37,140
Can we have that one?
我们能开那个吗

318
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:04,380
All we need is a banjo.
原来我们要找个非洲土著

319
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:06,780
Keep your voice down.
声音小点儿

320
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:09,100
Don't make any sudden moves.
别随便乱动

321
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:11,140
Just stay close to me.
紧跟着我

322
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:13,460
-Don't use your cell phone. -You took my cell phone.
-别用手机 -你已经把手机扔了

323
00:32:13,540 --> 00:32:16,540
Don't talk about cell phones. Don't talk about satellites.
别提手机 别提卫星

324
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:17,660
Seriously?
有这么严重吗

325
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:21,980
Why are you trying to kill me?
你为什么要杀我

326
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:23,900
I'm not trying to kill you!
我没想杀你

327
00:32:23,980 --> 00:32:25,060
Oh, yeah. You are.
别废话 你当然想

328
00:32:25,300 --> 00:32:26,580
Why would I be trying to kill you?
我为什么要杀你

329
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:29,180
Because the last time we met, I tried to kill you.
因为上次我们见面时 我要杀你

330
00:32:29,260 --> 00:32:30,500
That was a long time ago.
那已经很久了

331
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:32,980
Some people hold on to things like that.
有些人就是非常坚持

332
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:38,300
I'm not trying to kill you. Okay?
我不想杀你 好吗

333
00:32:39,820 --> 00:32:41,500
So that makes us friends.
我们和解好吗

334
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:42,820
Right?
好吗

335
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:45,660
Right.
好吧

336
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:47,020
Good.
很好

337
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:50,580
You wanna take that knife out of my balls now?
把刀从我裤裆拿开好吗

338
00:32:55,860 --> 00:32:56,940
Who is she?
她是谁

339
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,580
Sarah. She's not trying to kill you either.
莎拉 她也不会杀你的

340
00:33:02,020 --> 00:33:03,620
I don't stay in the open.
我从不待在露天处

341
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:08,660
Come on, I'll show you the house.
走吧 我带你到屋里转转

342
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:11,020
What's that?
那屋子算什么

343
00:33:12,100 --> 00:33:13,180
Decoy.
诱饵

344
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:19,380
He lives in a car?
他就住在小轿车里

345
00:33:24,020 --> 00:33:25,220
Come on in.
进来吧

346
00:33:35,060 --> 00:33:37,700
Why do you live here when you have the other place?
既然你有房子 为什么还住在这里

347
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:45,060
When the helicopter passed over the house last year
去年 直升机从这里飞过

348
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:48,380
and I could feel their eyes on me.
我就感觉他们盯上我了

349
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:52,180
Wet like peaches.
黑手无处不在

350
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,060
I have a list here.
我这里有张名单

351
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:59,180
It was written by a reporter who's now dead.
一个记者写的 然后被杀了

352
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:01,900
Along with everyone whose names are on that list.
受访的所有人名字都在名单上

353
00:34:02,060 --> 00:34:03,620
Well, almost everyone.
几乎所有人

354
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:07,500
Frank, how many times have I told you?
弗兰克 我告诉你多少遍了

355
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:09,740
You cannot trust the system!
绝不能相信体系

356
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:15,100
I told you when you're in the system, they switch the flip and you're done.
你进CIA时我就说了 他们一翻脸你就玩完

357
00:34:15,580 --> 00:34:18,900
Man, satellites, cell phones,
人哪 卫星 手机

358
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:23,340
chips, net, the web, the dentist...
芯片 网络 互联 牙医

359
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:24,580
Marvin!
马文

360
00:34:26,780 --> 00:34:29,900
That list is the one we need help with.
我们需要这份名单帮忙

361
00:34:30,220 --> 00:34:32,420
I gotta check the files.
我去调查一下

362
00:34:33,220 --> 00:34:34,940
Of course you do. Thanks, man.
当然了 谢谢你 伙计

363
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:44,620
This guy's insane.
这家伙疯了

364
00:34:44,900 --> 00:34:49,860
Well, he thought he was the subject of
a secret government mind control project.
他认为自己 被政府的一个思想控制项目秘密监控了

365
00:34:49,940 --> 00:34:51,140
This'll take a minute.
这得要几分钟

366
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:52,580
Sure.
当然

367
00:34:53,140 --> 00:34:54,700
As it turns out,
于是乎

368
00:34:55,380 --> 00:35:00,140
he really was being given daily doses of LSD for 11 years.
他还真每天吃 半人工致幻剂 吃了11 年

369
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:03,460
In that case, he looks great. -Fantastic.
若是十一年 那他精神倒挺好 -奇迹

370
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:07,500
Got it. Guatemala. Fall 1981.
好了 危地马拉 1981年秋

371
00:35:08,420 --> 00:35:13,020
Five of the guys on this list were there,
not including us.
除我们外 名单上有五个人当时都在那

372
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:15,780
San Benito. Just outside.
圣贝尼托 就在边上

373
00:35:16,180 --> 00:35:17,260
Injun territory.
印第安领土

374
00:35:17,460 --> 00:35:21,420
Was a little village.Everybody was killed. Civilians.
是个小村庄 所有人都被杀了 都是平民

375
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:23,220
They told us, "Go in there. Clean it up.
他们让我们 “深入 打扫干净”

376
00:35:23,340 --> 00:35:25,100
"Make it look like it never happened."
“就像什么都没有发生过”

377
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:27,860
You think everyone on this list was there?
你确认名单上所有人当时都在场吗

378
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,620
Damn it.
见鬼

379
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:32,180
Damn it!
天哪

380
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:34,900
Do you know what's wrong with this country?
你知道 这国家出什么毛病了吗

381
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:38,140
They're all trying to kill us?
他们都想干掉我们吗

382
00:35:38,340 --> 00:35:39,660
Exactly!
对极了

383
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:42,660
Is there anybody still alive on that list?
名单上还有人幸存吗

384
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,780
Gabriel Singer.
加布里尔·辛格

385
00:35:45,980 --> 00:35:47,140
Frank!
弗兰克

386
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:49,980
I never thought I'd say this again.
真不敢相信我又得来一遍

387
00:35:50,180 --> 00:35:51,980
I am getting the pig!
我得带上我的猪

388
00:35:59,860 --> 00:36:01,500
Who's she talking to?
她给谁打电话

389
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:04,180
Just take it easy.
别紧张

390
00:36:05,180 --> 00:36:07,380
Frank, we gotta get rid of this broad.
弗兰克 我们得避免这种大众通讯

391
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:10,180
I know a great place, just up the road. Lots of alligators.
我知道一个地方 就在路对面 很多鳄鱼

392
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:12,220
We're not getting rid of the broad.
我们不能不用这些东西

393
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:14,180
I like her.
我喜欢她

394
00:36:14,660 --> 00:36:16,780
What's the angle?
哪方面

395
00:36:17,820 --> 00:36:19,100
No angle. I like her.
没哪方面 就是喜欢

396
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:24,540
So, they pull her voice from the pay phone,
看吧 他们会从电话里提取她的声音

397
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:26,220
probably right now,
很可能就此时此刻

398
00:36:26,380 --> 00:36:29,460
install the recognition software and back-trace it to Singer.
通过语音识别软件 追踪到辛格

399
00:36:29,540 --> 00:36:32,620
So then we show up, they bring out the satellite,
我们一露头 他们就卫星定位

400
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:34,700
and we're fried with Y-rays.
我们就被激光枪瞄准了

401
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,380
How you doing?
还好吗

402
00:36:39,140 --> 00:36:40,420
Good, fine.
很好 谢谢

403
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:51,500
November niner 748.
N-9-748

404
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:55,140
Singer is going to be in Mobile tomorrow.
辛格明天会在 Mobile 当班

405
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:56,900
We can catch him at the airfreight terminal.
我们可以 在机场塔台 找到他

406
00:36:57,300 --> 00:36:58,300
How about that?
你们看怎么样

407
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:27,300
No, please! No!
住手 求你了

408
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:28,980
You smell like Washington.
你闻着像华府间谍

409
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:30,420
Who do you work for?
你为谁工作

410
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:32,940
Coldwell Banker, I'm a real estate agent! Please, don't hurt me.
寇威尔·班克 我只是个房产中介 求你 别伤害我

411
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:35,020
No, no. Who do you work for?
不对 不对 你到底是谁

412
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:36,820
Who do you work for?
哪个部门的

413
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:37,860
Marvin!
马文

414
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:41,020
Frank, she's one of them. She's been following us.
弗兰克 她是他们一伙的 她在跟踪我们

415
00:37:41,220 --> 00:37:44,260
There's a camera in her bag. I'm gonna kill her now.
她包里有摄像机 我得干掉她

416
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:46,780
No, please don't kill...Don't let him kill me! Please!
不 求你不要杀我…别让他杀我 求你了

417
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:50,300
Marvin, just wait, would you, please?
马文 等等 好吗 拜托了

418
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:52,020
Marvin. Look. Marvin.
马文 看看 马文

419
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:55,780
No camera in the bag.
包里没相机

420
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:58,660
Go, ma'am, now. Now.
走吧 女士 快走

421
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:05,060
Get a car.
找辆车

422
00:38:05,580 --> 00:38:06,820
Try not to kill anyone.
别让任何人送命

423
00:38:09,340 --> 00:38:11,580
She was following us, Frank.
她肯定在跟踪我们 弗兰克

424
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:25,940
Sorry.
抱歉

425
00:38:28,260 --> 00:38:31,860
"She has a camera in her purse, we have to kill her?"
她包里有相机 我们得干掉她

426
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,940
Seriously?
没开玩笑吧

427
00:38:39,700 --> 00:38:40,740
See you in a minute.
呆会儿见

428
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:46,860
Gabriel?
加布里尔

429
00:38:48,020 --> 00:38:49,620
Right? Gabriel Singer?
对吗 加布里尔·辛格

430
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:52,340
What's this about?
有什么事吗

431
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:56,180
Guatemala. 1981. San Benito.
危地马拉 1981年 圣贝尼托

432
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:57,340
I can't talk to you.
没什么好说的

433
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,620
Pair beats ace.
你们人多

434
00:39:07,060 --> 00:39:08,380
I got one for you.
我有个问题

435
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:11,980
What did this twice-decorated, west Texas Jew-boy Marine pilot
一个来自西得克萨斯的犹太男人 受过两次表彰的海军飞行员

436
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:14,260
say to the Chinese New York Times reporter?
会跟纽约时报的华裔记者说什么

437
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:15,380
I give up.
我不知道

438
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:18,420
Nothing. I didn't tell her a damn thing.
木有 我没透露给她任何东西

439
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:19,980
The reporter's dead now.
那记者已经死了

440
00:39:20,940 --> 00:39:23,620
And everyone she spoke to is either dead
or a target.
她采访过的人 也都死了 或成了目标

441
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:24,980
That includes you.
包括你

442
00:39:25,820 --> 00:39:26,900
Oh, Christ.
上帝啊

443
00:39:30,860 --> 00:39:33,540
They had me fly this guy out there in the dead of night.
那晚他们让我 带这个人飞出来

444
00:39:34,340 --> 00:39:36,500
Hairy little airstrip in the middle of nowhere.
路中间一条糟糕兮兮的跑道

445
00:39:37,060 --> 00:39:40,140
He was CIA, some dorky little spook in a suit and tie.
那人是CIA 傻乎乎的西装领带 寝食不安的样子

446
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:41,380
Remember that guy?
记得这家伙吗

447
00:39:41,460 --> 00:39:44,180
-Black glasses. -Yeah. He was giving the orders.
-墨镜那个 -就是他下的命令

448
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:46,260
He picked up a package and I flew him back out.
他收拾了东西 我带他出来

449
00:39:46,340 --> 00:39:47,340
What was the package?
收拾什么东西

450
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:48,740
It wasn't a what.
不是什么东西

451
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,020
It was a who.
是一个人

452
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:53,220
Frank! Frank!
弗兰克 弗兰克

453
00:39:53,500 --> 00:39:54,940
It's that helicopter.
那架直升机

454
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:57,220
We're in an airport. So...
我们在机场 当然…

455
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:58,940
It's the same helicopter.
是同一架直升机

456
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:04,420
November niner 748 Charlie.
N-9-748-C

457
00:40:04,700 --> 00:40:08,340
November niner 748 Charlie.
N-9-748-C

458
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:12,900
See? Frank, November niner 74...
对吧 弗兰克 N-9-74…

459
00:40:12,980 --> 00:40:14,020
Is that a 4?
那是 4  吗

460
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:15,460
This is a 4. Charlie.
这就是4 C

461
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:17,580
Is that a 7? What is that?
那是 7 吗 那是个什么

462
00:40:17,660 --> 00:40:19,220
I'll tell you what it is.
我跟你看看那是什么

463
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:31,340
I told you she shouldn't have made that phone call!
我跟你说了 她不该那么打电话

464
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:34,460
We lost visual on target.
视野内目标消失

465
00:40:34,540 --> 00:40:36,060
All right. Shake the tree.
好吧 毁掉整座房子

466
00:40:36,140 --> 00:40:38,380
-You'll pay for the breakage? -Yeah, Roger that.
-你赔钱吗 -收到 别废话

467
00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:02,260
That's right, old man!
你猜对了 老东西

468
00:41:03,940 --> 00:41:06,300
-Old man? -No respect.
-老东西 -真不尊重人

469
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:07,540
Can I kill her now?
现在我可以干掉她了吧

470
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:20,180
She called me an old man.
她骂我老东西

471
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:24,140
Pig! Open the pig!
猪猪 你的猪猪

472
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,220
Grenade!
手榴弹

473
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,060
Damn satellites!
去你的卫星

474
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:57,180
You just stay right there.
你就待那儿别动

475
00:41:57,300 --> 00:41:58,340
This is gonna be good.
这样就很好

476
00:42:14,420 --> 00:42:15,980
You okay?
你没事吧

477
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:22,700
What are you doing?
你要干什么

478
00:42:59,620 --> 00:43:01,340
Old man, my ass.
骂我老 吃屎吧

479
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:02,500
God damn it!
该死的

480
00:43:03,420 --> 00:43:06,300
-Smoke and thermals. Obstructed view. -Signal's fading.
-烟雾高温 视野受阻 -信号衰落

481
00:43:08,900 --> 00:43:10,300
Nice shot.
枪神在世啊

482
00:43:10,900 --> 00:43:13,180
-Thanks. -We should get out of here.
-谢谢 -我们得离开这里

483
00:43:31,980 --> 00:43:35,460
You really know how to show a girl a good time, Frank.
真有你的 知道在女人面前秀一把的时机 弗兰克

484
00:43:35,540 --> 00:43:37,140
I will kill you, Marvin.
闭上嘴 马文

485
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:41,980
Take it easy, man. She likes you.
放松伙计 她喜欢你

486
00:43:48,220 --> 00:43:49,620
How can you tell?
你怎么知道

487
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:54,300
Notice how she sticks around?
没看到她老跟着你吗

488
00:43:54,460 --> 00:43:57,700
'Cause if women don't like you, they don't stick around.
如果女人不喜欢你 她们不会跟着你

489
00:43:58,020 --> 00:44:00,180
She doesn't have much of a choice. Does she?
她别无选择 不是吗

490
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:01,700
Sure she does.
当然可以

491
00:44:03,380 --> 00:44:05,020
Really?
真的吗

492
00:44:05,620 --> 00:44:06,860
You think so?
你这么觉得

493
00:44:12,140 --> 00:44:14,260
You know, if it is the CIA,
你明白的 如果真是中情局

494
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:17,660
then there's only one place that we can go
那么就只有一个地方

495
00:44:17,740 --> 00:44:19,860
to find out why they're coming after us.
能查清他们为什么追杀我们

496
00:44:21,180 --> 00:44:23,420
We're gonna get killed there, for sure.
去那儿也等于自杀 当然了

497
00:44:24,380 --> 00:44:25,460
In or out?
干不干

498
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:28,420
No. Of course I'm in. I'm just saying.
当然干了 我只是唠叨 两句

499
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:33,540
We're gonna need some serious help.
我们需要一些靠谱的支援

500
00:44:36,140 --> 00:44:39,700
This is not the kind of help I meant, Frank.
这不是我说的那种支援 弗兰克

501
00:44:41,220 --> 00:44:43,500
You're not actually gonna go in there, are you?
你不是真要进去吧

502
00:44:46,220 --> 00:44:47,780
I don't think I can go, Frank.
我不敢进去 弗兰克

503
00:44:47,860 --> 00:44:54,340
The last time they put some electrical wires in some not very nice places.
上回 他们把电线 缠在匪夷所思的地方

504
00:44:59,420 --> 00:45:01,460
Listen, hang onto that for me.
听着 帮我拿着这个

505
00:45:04,940 --> 00:45:06,380
I'll be right back.
我很快就回来

506
00:45:17,260 --> 00:45:18,300
Be careful.
小心

507
00:45:43,740 --> 00:45:47,780
Tell Ivan Simanov that Frank Moses is...
通知伊万·西曼诺夫 弗兰克·摩西

508
00:45:47,860 --> 00:45:49,980
Frank Moses is here to see him.
弗兰克·摩西来了

509
00:46:04,300 --> 00:46:06,420
I have to say
不得不说

510
00:46:06,820 --> 00:46:14,260
this is the last thing I expected …… when I got up this morning.
这是今早醒来以后 …我最没预料到的事

511
00:46:19,820 --> 00:46:23,740
I have many times dreamed of killing you.
多少次 我做梦都想杀了你

512
00:46:25,220 --> 00:46:34,520
But now …you are …a pensioner.
现在呢…你…都领养老金了

513
00:46:36,980 --> 00:46:38,700
Couple of years now.
都两年了

514
00:46:39,100 --> 00:46:44,700
Time passes. As we get older, things seem less important.
时过境迁 当我们老去 很多事看上去都不那么重要了

515
00:46:46,060 --> 00:46:54,020
Still …I owe you …for killing Igor.
但…我欠你…你除掉了伊戈尔

516
00:46:54,580 --> 00:46:56,660
-Igor the Butcher. -He was a great asset.
-屠夫伊戈尔 -他是笔巨大的财富

517
00:46:56,740 --> 00:46:59,740
-He was a pig. -He was my cousin.
-他就是头猪 -他是我表弟

518
00:47:00,980 --> 00:47:02,020
I'm sorry.
我很抱歉

519
00:47:12,900 --> 00:47:16,540
To Igor. The Butcher.
敬伊戈尔 屠夫

520
00:47:17,700 --> 00:47:22,940
He's not dead. I flipped him.
他没死 我掉包了

521
00:47:24,020 --> 00:47:25,100
No.
不会吧

522
00:47:25,260 --> 00:47:27,500
He owns a string of 7-Elevens in Orange County.
他现在香桔市 开 7-11 连锁店

523
00:47:28,740 --> 00:47:29,980
He weighs 500 pounds.
他500磅重

524
00:47:43,500 --> 00:47:44,580
Drink.
干杯

525
00:47:45,740 --> 00:47:47,140
Who are we drinking to now?
这杯敬谁

526
00:47:48,540 --> 00:47:49,740
Veronique.
维罗妮卡

527
00:47:51,580 --> 00:47:54,300
She was mine.
她是我的

528
00:47:55,420 --> 00:47:57,060
-Impossible. -Yes!
-不可思议 -是啊

529
00:48:05,180 --> 00:48:06,740
Whatever she got, it was worth it.
不管她去哪儿了 这都值了

530
00:48:11,460 --> 00:48:12,820
I miss the old days.
真怀念老时候啊

531
00:48:16,900 --> 00:48:20,780
I haven't killed anyone in years.
我都好几年没杀人了

532
00:48:22,660 --> 00:48:23,900
That's sad.
好可怜

533
00:48:29,140 --> 00:48:34,780
But …I think you are not here for the vodka.
不过 我觉得你不是来喝伏特加的吧

534
00:48:39,420 --> 00:48:41,340
I'm going to break into the CIA.
我要闯进中情局

535
00:48:42,580 --> 00:48:45,060
I need your complete security layout of Langley.
我需要你提供 兰利完整的安全布局

536
00:48:45,620 --> 00:48:48,780
Cracks. Codes. ID swipes.
漏洞 密码 身份识别卡

537
00:48:49,780 --> 00:48:50,900
All of it.
所有东西

538
00:48:52,980 --> 00:48:56,060
Amusing as this would be,
虽然这很有趣

539
00:48:57,020 --> 00:49:00,060
it is beyond my reach.
不过超出我能力范围了

540
00:49:07,260 --> 00:49:10,460
A favor from Frank Moses?
弗兰克·摩西求我了 哇

541
00:49:20,980 --> 00:49:23,420
I can't believe you're actually letting me come along.
真不敢相信 你竟然让我过来了

542
00:49:24,020 --> 00:49:27,100
The badges Ivan gave us are for a General Harlow
伊万给的徽章 是哈罗将军

543
00:49:27,180 --> 00:49:30,300
and a female nuclear physicist from Los Alamos.
和阿拉莫斯实验室的女核物理学家的

544
00:49:35,460 --> 00:49:36,540
You're adopted.
接受

545
00:49:41,940 --> 00:49:44,340
This is so cool.
好酷啊

546
00:50:02,780 --> 00:50:03,820
What?
怎么了

547
00:50:04,220 --> 00:50:06,380
I dropped it.
掉地上了

548
00:50:08,940 --> 00:50:10,300
Freeze!
不许动

549
00:50:13,980 --> 00:50:16,380
The General has dropped his contact lens.
将军的隐形眼镜掉了

550
00:50:18,460 --> 00:50:20,460
Perhaps you'd like to help us?
能帮我们找找吗

551
00:50:22,500 --> 00:50:23,980
Sorry.
对不起

552
00:50:30,340 --> 00:50:32,780
Found it! I found it!
找到了 我找到了

553
00:50:33,820 --> 00:50:35,340
I found it.
我找到了

554
00:50:48,900 --> 00:50:50,460
Have a good day, sir.
工作愉快 长官

555
00:50:50,980 --> 00:50:52,220
Gentlemen.
先生们

556
00:50:53,100 --> 00:50:54,420
My God!
天哪

557
00:50:56,660 --> 00:51:00,340
What do you suppose the punishment is for what we're doing here?
你有没有想过 如果失败了会被怎样

558
00:51:00,940 --> 00:51:02,260
Death.
死刑

559
00:51:03,580 --> 00:51:04,780
Maybe life in prison.
或终身监禁

560
00:51:04,980 --> 00:51:06,340
Awesome.
棒极了

561
00:51:13,140 --> 00:51:14,940
Why are you holding that button?
为什么按那个按钮

562
00:51:25,100 --> 00:51:26,700
The Russians give you the code?
俄罗斯人给你密码了

563
00:51:27,260 --> 00:51:28,340
No.
没有

564
00:51:29,540 --> 00:51:31,540
Changes every six hours.
密码每六小时会换

565
00:51:31,940 --> 00:51:33,260
Will you hold that for me for a second?
能帮我拿一下吗

566
00:51:37,820 --> 00:51:39,300
It's unbreakable.
这是坚不可摧的

567
00:51:47,820 --> 00:51:48,980
Come on.
来吧

568
00:52:02,620 --> 00:52:04,060
Mr. Moses!
摩西先生

569
00:52:05,340 --> 00:52:07,100
Been a long time.
好久不见了

570
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:09,620
I'm gonna need to see that Guatemala file.
我来查看一下 危地马拉的档案

571
00:52:09,980 --> 00:52:11,140
Guatemala?
危地马拉

572
00:52:14,300 --> 00:52:15,660
I think I can help you.
我想我能帮上忙

573
00:52:16,820 --> 00:52:17,980
Great.
太好了

574
00:52:22,220 --> 00:52:25,180
It's been a whole new world around here since you left.
你离开后 这里都改天换地了

575
00:52:27,220 --> 00:52:28,340
Guatemala.
危地马拉

576
00:52:33,020 --> 00:52:34,220
You know, you're gonna catch hell for this.
你要知道 你可能因此下地狱的

577
00:52:34,380 --> 00:52:35,940
After what I've seen?
我看过之后吗

578
00:52:38,340 --> 00:52:39,860
Oh, I should tell you,
对了 有点事你得知道

579
00:52:40,140 --> 00:52:43,340
there's a new guy came down here yesterday looking for your file.
昨天一个新家伙过来看你的资料

580
00:52:43,540 --> 00:52:46,220
Name of William Cooper?
叫什么 威廉·库珀

581
00:52:47,100 --> 00:52:49,340
6'1"? Cute hair?
高六尺一 可爱的头发

582
00:52:50,500 --> 00:52:51,620
Hair was cute.
头发的确挺逗的

583
00:52:53,020 --> 00:52:55,100
But I thought he looked a little tough, though.
尽管如此 我看他也算个难缠货呢

584
00:52:58,460 --> 00:53:00,020
You take good care of yourself, Henry.
自己多保重 亨利

585
00:53:00,380 --> 00:53:02,220
You, too, Mr. Moses.
你也是 摩西先生

586
00:53:05,380 --> 00:53:06,380
Change of plan.
计划有变

587
00:53:23,340 --> 00:53:24,700
Bad move, Grandpa.
来错了 老爷爷

588
00:54:11,260 --> 00:54:12,340
Kordesky trained you?
柯德斯基 训练你的吗

589
00:54:13,580 --> 00:54:15,100
I trained Kordesky.
我训练的柯德斯基

590
00:54:38,820 --> 00:54:39,940
Son of a bitch!
狗娘养的

591
00:54:46,020 --> 00:54:48,100
Seal the building. Bald, white male, 50s,
封锁大楼 光头 白种男性 五十来岁

592
00:54:48,180 --> 00:54:50,660
wearing white shirt, blue pants, shot in the shoulder.
白衬衣 蓝裤子 肩部中枪

593
00:55:00,500 --> 00:55:01,540
We should go.
我们得走了

594
00:55:02,300 --> 00:55:03,380
We should go now.
现在就得走

595
00:55:31,300 --> 00:55:33,700
I've got checkpoints at every exit. What about the fire?
每个出口都有检查点 火灾怎么办

596
00:55:33,820 --> 00:55:36,420
Shut off the alarm. I told you, there is no fire!
关掉警报 我告诉你了 根本没火灾

597
00:55:38,700 --> 00:55:41,100
-We need to evacuate. -No, this is just a diversion.
-我们得紧急疏散 -不 这是调虎离山

598
00:55:41,180 --> 00:55:42,860
You make sure everyone gets checked.
确保每个人都接受检查

599
00:55:44,780 --> 00:55:48,340
Help, help! Please come!
救命 救命 快到这边

600
00:55:48,980 --> 00:55:50,820
I can't stop the bleeding.
他不停的流血

601
00:55:55,580 --> 00:55:56,700
You okay, sir?
你没事吧 先生

602
00:55:57,100 --> 00:55:58,180
Make a hole!
让一下

603
00:55:58,660 --> 00:55:59,980
Make a hole!
让一下

604
00:56:00,380 --> 00:56:02,740
Hold it. Let me see him.
等一下 让我看一下

605
00:56:03,980 --> 00:56:05,020
It's not him.
不是他

606
00:56:09,620 --> 00:56:11,100
Fellas, help me out, here.
伙计们 搭把手

607
00:56:29,780 --> 00:56:31,020
Marvin?
马文

608
00:56:37,220 --> 00:56:39,460
There's still something wrong with this guy's head, Frank.
这家伙脑袋还是不大清醒 弗兰克

609
00:56:45,900 --> 00:56:47,540
You're really something, Joe.
真有你的 乔

610
00:56:48,420 --> 00:56:49,580
Marvin, you okay?
马文 你没事吧

611
00:56:49,740 --> 00:56:51,220
I don't want to talk about it.
我不想说这事儿

612
00:56:53,900 --> 00:56:56,180
Joe? Joe who was dead Joe?
乔 死了的那个乔

613
00:56:57,060 --> 00:56:58,620
She with us?
她是一块儿的吗

614
00:56:59,940 --> 00:57:01,140
Not dead.
没死

615
00:57:03,300 --> 00:57:04,420
Just retired.
只是退休了

616
00:57:10,380 --> 00:57:11,860
I guess calling wasn't an option?
你不能先打个电话吗

617
00:57:11,940 --> 00:57:13,740
Can we go?
可以走了吗

618
00:57:13,940 --> 00:57:15,140
You let yourself get shot?
你怎么挨枪子儿了

619
00:57:16,020 --> 00:57:17,180
God damn it.
该死的

620
00:57:18,700 --> 00:57:19,860
Out.
出去

621
00:57:20,820 --> 00:57:22,220
-You okay? -Thanks, Doc.
-没事吧 -谢谢医生

622
00:57:22,580 --> 00:57:23,740
What did he get?
他偷走了什么

623
00:57:26,940 --> 00:57:28,700
I have no idea.
我不知道

624
00:57:29,460 --> 00:57:33,780
You just had your ass handed to you by a goddamn retiree.
你刚刚 被一个该死的退休人员 揍了一顿

625
00:57:35,860 --> 00:57:37,260
What did he do?
他究竟是谁

626
00:57:39,500 --> 00:57:41,940
What did Moses do to earn a lethal finding?
摩西究竟做了什么 招来这杀身之祸

627
00:57:42,020 --> 00:57:44,260
I have not been read into it.
我没研究过

628
00:57:44,820 --> 00:57:47,460
I like you, Cooper. You're ambitious and you get results,
我很欣赏你 库珀 你雄心勃勃干到现在

629
00:57:47,660 --> 00:57:50,580
but someone just kicked in the front door of our house,
但现在 有人已经踢爆咱们家前大门了

630
00:57:50,660 --> 00:57:52,780
so you better get your shit straight.
你最好振作起来 做好自己的事

631
00:57:53,140 --> 00:57:55,460
Nothing in your mission is changed.
你的任务 没有任何改变

632
00:57:58,380 --> 00:57:59,900
You're still bleeding.
你还在流血

633
00:58:00,660 --> 00:58:02,460
Must have nicked something in there.
一定是皮下有伤口了

634
00:58:02,820 --> 00:58:04,380
This is so bad.
这太糟糕了

635
00:58:04,460 --> 00:58:07,500
It's not that bad. People get shot all the time.
不算太糟 人们随时都会中枪的

636
00:58:07,580 --> 00:58:09,860
No, they don't, they get paper cuts.
胡说 常人只是被纸割伤手指

637
00:58:09,980 --> 00:58:11,180
I mostly get shot.
我就经常中弹

638
00:58:11,260 --> 00:58:14,220
We're gonna have to find somebody to plug this leak.
我们得找个人缝补伤口

639
00:58:19,300 --> 00:58:20,980
Could go to Eagle's Nest.
那就去鹰巢吧

640
00:58:22,660 --> 00:58:24,020
Then we all get shot.
那我们就都要挨枪子儿了

641
00:58:25,660 --> 00:58:27,180
I'll just go in by myself.
我自己进去吧

642
00:58:28,140 --> 00:58:29,180
Want a vest?
要穿件马甲吗

643
00:58:32,260 --> 00:58:33,780
Wouldn't do any good.
那只会坏事

644
00:59:10,380 --> 00:59:11,700
Frank Moses.
弗兰克·摩西

645
00:59:13,020 --> 00:59:14,340
Hi, Victoria.
你好 维多利亚

646
00:59:19,420 --> 00:59:21,020
Are you here to kill me?
你来杀我吗

647
00:59:22,220 --> 00:59:23,300
No.
不是

648
00:59:27,460 --> 00:59:28,740
You've been shot.
你中枪了

649
00:59:37,180 --> 00:59:39,660
Tell Marvin to stand down before he gets hurt.
让马文老实呆着 别伤着自己

650
00:59:49,820 --> 00:59:51,100
Who's the girl?
这女孩儿是谁

651
00:59:51,580 --> 00:59:52,580
She's with me.
跟我一起的

652
00:59:52,900 --> 00:59:54,580
-Vicky. -Joe!
-维琪 -乔

653
00:59:54,660 --> 00:59:57,620
Oh, Vicky. Sexy as ever.
维琪 还是性感依旧啊

654
00:59:59,580 --> 01:00:02,580
You old snake charmer.
你个英俊的老滑头

655
01:00:02,900 --> 01:00:06,580
Sarah, this is Victoria. Best wet work asset in the business.
莎拉 这是维多利亚 业界最佳能手

656
01:00:06,820 --> 01:00:09,180
And a true artist with an RPN.
堪称 严谨操作 的艺术家

657
01:00:09,300 --> 01:00:10,820
What's that?
什么意思

658
01:00:12,380 --> 01:00:13,940
I kill people, dear.
意味我杀人 亲爱的

659
01:00:17,180 --> 01:00:18,420
You were lucky.
你走运了

660
01:00:25,460 --> 01:00:26,900
How'd you do it?
你怎么做到的

661
01:00:27,620 --> 01:00:30,260
-What? -How'd you make the transition?
什么 你怎么过渡过来的

662
01:00:30,740 --> 01:00:33,900
Here you seem so calm. At ease.
你看起来是如此平静 平静如水

663
01:00:35,140 --> 01:00:36,420
I love it.
我爱这生活

664
01:00:36,940 --> 01:00:41,020
I love it here. I love the baking. I love the flower arranging.
我爱这里 我爱甜饼 我爱周围的花朵

665
01:00:41,620 --> 01:00:43,140
I like the routine.
我喜欢有条不紊

666
01:00:49,500 --> 01:00:52,700
I do get a bit restless sometimes.
我有时候真有些坐立不安

667
01:00:56,540 --> 01:00:59,700
I take the odd contract on the side.
我接另一边的活儿干

668
01:01:02,660 --> 01:01:03,740
I just can't stop.
我停不下来

669
01:01:05,300 --> 01:01:08,700
Yeah. Tell me about it.
跟我聊聊这个

670
01:01:08,780 --> 01:01:11,260
You can't just flip a switch and become someone else.
人们不能一扭头就成为另一个人

671
01:01:11,500 --> 01:01:12,860
Put some pressure on it.
好好按住这里

672
01:01:18,940 --> 01:01:20,460
Tell me about your lady friend.
跟我聊聊你的女朋友

673
01:01:22,580 --> 01:01:30,540
Makes me think that I could actually have a life.
她让我觉得我可以拥有生活

674
01:01:31,700 --> 01:01:32,900
A real life.
真正的生活

675
01:01:33,020 --> 01:01:36,260
Oh, Francis, you're such a romantic.
弗兰克 你真是浪漫

676
01:01:36,540 --> 01:01:37,620
What?
什么

677
01:01:37,700 --> 01:01:39,940
A romantic. It's why I've always been so fond of you.
罗曼蒂克 这也是为什么我一直挺喜欢你的

678
01:01:40,020 --> 01:01:41,020
Victoria...
维多利亚

679
01:01:41,100 --> 01:01:43,780
You're all hard on the outside, but you are...
你外表强悍 但你…

680
01:01:44,780 --> 01:01:46,740
You are gooey on the inside.
内心里多愁善感

681
01:01:49,820 --> 01:01:51,220
Gooey.
多愁善感

682
01:01:52,940 --> 01:01:57,300
The entire back half of the Guatemala file has been blacked out.
危地马拉的档案 几乎全被涂黑了

683
01:01:58,060 --> 01:02:02,140
But there's a list. 11 names. Plus one that's been redacted.
但这张名单 11个人 多了个档案里删减的

684
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:04,940
All dead. Except for Frank and Marvin.
他们全死了 除了弗兰克和马文

685
01:02:05,220 --> 01:02:07,940
All the names on the reporter's list are in the file, too,
记者名单上的人 也都出现在档案里

686
01:02:08,020 --> 01:02:09,940
but she has an additional name.
但她额外提到一个人

687
01:02:10,380 --> 01:02:11,540
Alexander Dunning.
亚历山大·丹宁

688
01:02:12,220 --> 01:02:13,820
Somebody's protecting him.
有人在保护他

689
01:02:14,660 --> 01:02:18,340
Dunning is the CEO of Browning-Orvis.
丹宁是 布朗宁-奥维斯 的总裁

690
01:02:18,540 --> 01:02:19,580
Gangsters.
黑帮

691
01:02:20,060 --> 01:02:21,140
Defense contractor.
国防承包商

692
01:02:21,580 --> 01:02:22,620
Very connected.
非常接近了

693
01:02:24,100 --> 01:02:29,460
If the CIA is protecting him, he's under surveillance.
如果中情局在保护他 他一定被严密监视

694
01:02:29,780 --> 01:02:30,860
We could go see him.
我们可以去找他

695
01:02:31,060 --> 01:02:32,420
You're not going without me.
没我你哪儿也不能去

696
01:02:34,620 --> 01:02:37,740
We're getting the band back together. That's nice.
我们又重新在一起了 棒极了

697
01:03:02,460 --> 01:03:03,500
Yeah?
什么事

698
01:03:03,620 --> 01:03:06,100
We just got a tip. RED has a new target.
我们刚收到提醒 RED有新目标了

699
01:03:06,780 --> 01:03:07,780
A tip?
一个提醒

700
01:03:08,860 --> 01:03:10,060
FBI's on the scene.
联邦调查局介入了

701
01:03:10,260 --> 01:03:11,580
I'm on my way.
我马上到

702
01:03:23,300 --> 01:03:26,300
The FBI has a lookout position on the east perimeter.
FBI 在东边布防一个监视岗

703
01:03:27,020 --> 01:03:28,100
Copy that.
收到

704
01:03:51,820 --> 01:03:53,340
Alexander Dunning.
亚历山大·丹宁

705
01:03:53,460 --> 01:03:56,180
Pleasure to see you, Secretary Baptiste.
很高兴见到您 巴蒂斯特秘书长

706
01:03:56,260 --> 01:03:58,020
The pleasure is with me.
也很高兴见到你

707
01:04:02,900 --> 01:04:04,180
They're in.
他们进屋了

708
01:04:05,980 --> 01:04:07,860
Frank said you wanted me with you.
弗兰克说你想让我跟着你

709
01:04:08,180 --> 01:04:10,980
Yes, I thought it might be nice to have a bit of girl time together.
是啊 我想 有一小段闺蜜时光 会很美妙

710
01:04:12,620 --> 01:04:14,020
Get to know each other.
相互了解对方

711
01:04:15,860 --> 01:04:20,300
And I just wanted to tell you that in all the years I've known Francis,
我只是想告诉你 我认识弗兰克这么多年了

712
01:04:21,340 --> 01:04:22,860
I've never seen him like this.
从没见过他像现在这样

713
01:04:25,740 --> 01:04:29,300
So if you break his heart, I will kill you.
所以 如果你伤了他的心 我就杀了你

714
01:04:29,820 --> 01:04:31,660
And bury your body in the woods.
把你的尸体扔在烂树丛里

715
01:04:39,740 --> 01:04:41,700
Oh, this is gonna be fun.
哦 这会很好玩的

716
01:04:45,940 --> 01:04:47,940
Here at Browning-Orvis,
在布朗宁-奥维斯

717
01:04:48,220 --> 01:04:52,260
we have a longstanding commitment to humanitarian causes
我们长期致力于人道主义

718
01:04:52,420 --> 01:04:56,900
because exemplary corporate citizenship is our highest calling.
因为 成为企业公民 是我们的最高使命

719
01:04:57,180 --> 01:05:00,780
As a company with global reach and global interests,
作为 具有全球影响力 和全球利益的大公司

720
01:05:00,860 --> 01:05:03,900
we have global responsibilities.
我们也有全球的责任

721
01:05:05,140 --> 01:05:06,660
Now sometimes I'm asked,
现在如果有人问我

722
01:05:06,860 --> 01:05:11,060
if this commitment to ethical behavior affects the bottom line.
如果人道主义的承诺 影响到了底线怎么办

723
01:05:11,260 --> 01:05:14,060
And my answer is always the same.
我的回答依然不变

724
01:05:14,300 --> 01:05:15,340
Yes.
是的

725
01:05:15,940 --> 01:05:17,980
It makes it stronger.
使命使公司强大

726
01:05:18,220 --> 01:05:22,220
This is my safe room. Sound-proofed. Reinforced.
这是我的安全屋 完美隔音 钢混建造

727
01:05:22,500 --> 01:05:24,300
Swept for bugs daily.
每天清清蟑螂

728
01:05:24,580 --> 01:05:28,100
You could fire a gun in here. No one would ever know.
在这儿放一枪 没人听得到

729
01:05:28,740 --> 01:05:30,180
Mr. Dunning.
丹宁先生

730
01:05:31,740 --> 01:05:35,420
I cannot imagine a more perfect place to conduct our business.
这实在是我们谈生意的最好地方了

731
01:05:39,300 --> 01:05:41,380
You do know that there's
你应该很清楚

732
01:05:42,260 --> 01:05:45,900
a surcharge for any arms deliveries
向联合国武器禁运国输送武器

733
01:05:46,340 --> 01:05:49,460
to countries that are embargoed by the United Nations.
是要另收附加费的

734
01:05:50,820 --> 01:05:55,180
For every problem, monsieur, there is a solution.
任何问题 我的先生 都会有答案的

735
01:05:59,620 --> 01:06:01,180
Excuse me.
抱歉 稍等

736
01:06:12,220 --> 01:06:13,980
So how did you guys meet?
你们俩怎么认识的

737
01:06:15,260 --> 01:06:17,420
We started talking on the phone.
刚开始我们通电话

738
01:06:18,980 --> 01:06:21,700
I guess I liked that it wasn't real.
我大概 太喜欢虚幻了

739
01:06:23,460 --> 01:06:24,580
Of course now I'm a fugitive,
当然我现在在逃亡

740
01:06:24,660 --> 01:06:27,340
the CIA wants to kill me and I'm hiding in a hole.
中情局要我的命 我东藏西躲的

741
01:06:29,140 --> 01:06:32,500
I was in love with an agent once.
从前我和一名特工相爱

742
01:06:33,660 --> 01:06:34,980
What happened?
然后呢

743
01:06:36,340 --> 01:06:38,420
Well, I was with MI6.
当时我是军情六处的

744
01:06:38,620 --> 01:06:42,620
And the relationship wasn't sanctioned.
我们的关系不被认可

745
01:06:44,820 --> 01:06:47,860
So when it came to light, my loyalty was questioned.
后来事情浮出水面 我的忠诚面临抉择

746
01:06:48,020 --> 01:06:49,500
And I was ordered to kill him.
我受命要杀了他

747
01:06:50,100 --> 01:06:51,300
It was a test.
这是个考验

748
01:06:52,340 --> 01:06:53,820
What did you do?
你怎么做了

749
01:06:55,460 --> 01:06:57,700
I put three bullets in his chest.
我在他肩膀上打了三颗子弹

750
01:07:01,740 --> 01:07:03,420
Who the hell are you guys?
你们他妈的是谁

751
01:07:03,660 --> 01:07:04,980
You don't remember us?
不记得我们了

752
01:07:06,180 --> 01:07:07,340
We remember you.
我们可记得你

753
01:07:08,820 --> 01:07:12,180
You're the guy whose shit we cleaned up down in Guatemala in 1981.
1981年 我们在危地马拉 给你擦屁股

754
01:07:15,260 --> 01:07:19,060
And the question is, who did you fly out of there?
问题是 你从那里弄出来的是谁

755
01:07:19,500 --> 01:07:22,940
You don't have any idea what you're getting into.
你们 根本不懂 自己卷入的什么

756
01:07:24,620 --> 01:07:27,660
First of all, you can't touch me.
首先 你动不了我

757
01:07:27,900 --> 01:07:29,100
Sure, we can.
当然能了

758
01:07:42,620 --> 01:07:43,860
Where'd you get this?
这个从哪儿弄得

759
01:07:44,060 --> 01:07:45,380
Home Depot.
家得宝

760
01:07:45,660 --> 01:07:48,180
-How much? -Ten bucks.
-多少钱 -十块

761
01:07:49,060 --> 01:07:53,740
You want nuts?  Nipples? Potty trainer?
你要坚果夹 钳子 还是通便器

762
01:07:54,620 --> 01:07:55,900
All right, stop it.
好啦 快住手

763
01:07:56,100 --> 01:07:57,140
Nuts.
坚果夹

764
01:07:58,060 --> 01:08:01,100
Stop it. For the love of Christ, stop it!
住手 看在上帝份上 住手

765
01:08:04,580 --> 01:08:05,740
Now you got something to say?
你现在有话要说吗

766
01:08:09,140 --> 01:08:12,380
We extracted a young lieutenant
我们救出了一名年轻上尉

767
01:08:12,580 --> 01:08:18,100
who is the son of the late Senator, James Stanton.
已故参议员 詹姆斯·斯坦顿的儿子

768
01:08:22,260 --> 01:08:23,420
Robert Stanton?
罗伯特·斯坦顿

769
01:08:23,620 --> 01:08:25,900
Vice President of the United States.
美国副总统

770
01:08:26,140 --> 01:08:29,900
You're saying the Vice President killed all the people in that village?
你的意思 是副总统 杀了全村百姓

771
01:08:29,980 --> 01:08:32,780
Went completely off the reservation.
事先完全没有通知

772
01:08:32,900 --> 01:08:34,900
And that New York Times reporter?
纽约时报那个记者

773
01:08:35,580 --> 01:08:36,740
Did she pressure you?
她给你施压了

774
01:08:36,900 --> 01:08:39,300
Yeah. She called me. Twice.
是 她打电话给我 两次

775
01:08:40,020 --> 01:08:41,500
So I called the V.P.
所以我通知了副总统

776
01:08:41,660 --> 01:08:44,500
And what did you think would happen then?
那你觉得 副总统会怎么做

777
01:08:44,660 --> 01:08:46,100
Oh, whatever.
管他呢

778
01:08:46,700 --> 01:08:48,300
I made him Vice President.
我让他当的副总统

779
01:08:48,580 --> 01:08:52,580
You kept your mouth shut and the Stantons made you rich.
你闭口不谈 斯坦顿让你发财

780
01:09:02,460 --> 01:09:05,300
I will pay whatever it costs
随便开个价

781
01:09:05,820 --> 01:09:07,260
to get rid of this thing.
我们了结了这事

782
01:09:08,660 --> 01:09:10,500
We're not here for your money, home.
我们来这里不是为了你的臭钱和房子

783
01:09:10,740 --> 01:09:14,340
We're here because that New York Times reporter had the list of names
我们来这里是因为 纽约时报的记者有张名单

784
01:09:14,580 --> 01:09:16,780
of everybody who was in Guatemala.
参加危地马拉任务的人都榜上有名

785
01:09:16,980 --> 01:09:20,060
And everybody on that list has been ordered killed.
而名单上的所有人 都被人安排杀害了

786
01:09:20,260 --> 01:09:21,420
Except you.
除了你

787
01:09:23,020 --> 01:09:24,700
I had nothing to do with that.
我与此毫无关系

788
01:09:26,620 --> 01:09:28,300
Don't you see?
还不明白吗

789
01:09:28,780 --> 01:09:33,860
He's trying to clean up his past and get rid of me in one shot.
他在尽力洗清他的过去 并一脚把我踢开

790
01:09:34,340 --> 01:09:37,740
He's trying to cut me loose before he runs for President.
试图在竞选总统之前 切断与我的所有关系

791
01:09:38,020 --> 01:09:40,060
We have some major activity out here.
外边有大批警力活动

792
01:09:40,620 --> 01:09:41,740
Looks like we're blown.
貌似我们要恶战了

793
01:09:58,300 --> 01:10:01,020
We're in position. Perimeter's set. No one's getting out.
全体就位 方圆内 任何人都出不来

794
01:10:05,180 --> 01:10:06,860
They're moving a team up the east side.
他们派一小队到东边驻守

795
01:10:07,060 --> 01:10:08,500
Are you gonna let me talk to them?
你们打算让我跟他们谈谈吗

796
01:10:08,580 --> 01:10:10,620
I can negotiate something.
我有资本跟他们谈判

797
01:10:10,780 --> 01:10:13,580
Thanks, when we want your help, we'll get out the drain cleaner.
谢谢 如果有必要 我会拿出通便器的

798
01:10:13,780 --> 01:10:15,860
Listen, Plastic Man,
听着 塑料人

799
01:10:15,940 --> 01:10:19,460
those bastards out there probably have orders to kill me, too.
外边那全混蛋 很有可能也要杀了我

800
01:10:19,660 --> 01:10:20,700
I hope so.
正合我意

801
01:10:20,940 --> 01:10:24,340
Why? 'Cause I'm a bad guy?
为什么 因为我是坏蛋

802
01:10:25,100 --> 01:10:26,500
I'm scum?
我是人渣

803
01:10:26,700 --> 01:10:28,180
Can I just shoot him now?
我能现在就崩了他吗

804
01:10:28,380 --> 01:10:29,540
No.
不行

805
01:10:29,780 --> 01:10:32,220
You don't have people killed.
你没必要杀人

806
01:10:32,460 --> 01:10:36,900
I have people killed, I'm the bad guy. Remember?
要杀人的是我 我演坏人 记得吗

807
01:10:42,460 --> 01:10:43,900
Not worth a bullet.
根本不值一颗子弹

808
01:10:53,500 --> 01:10:54,660
How's retirement, Frank?
退休生活怎么样 弗兰克

809
01:10:55,180 --> 01:10:56,740
It's been a real blast.
惊爆透了

810
01:10:56,860 --> 01:10:59,300
If we have to come in there and get you, it's gonna be messy.
如果我们强攻抓你 会一团糟的

811
01:10:59,660 --> 01:11:02,180
You bet. Real messy.
你说对了 糟透了

812
01:11:02,620 --> 01:11:04,180
I've got my orders, Frank.
我已经接到命令了 弗兰克

813
01:11:04,540 --> 01:11:06,100
They come from the Vice President.
命令是副总统下的

814
01:11:06,380 --> 01:11:10,060
He's ordered these hits to cover up the war crimes he committed in Guatemala.
他安排这一切 掩盖曾经在危地马拉犯下的战罪

815
01:11:10,260 --> 01:11:11,740
I find that hard to believe.
这很难让我信服

816
01:11:11,940 --> 01:11:13,940
How did you know you'd find me here?
那你是怎么找到我的呢

817
01:11:14,020 --> 01:11:16,340
Some anonymous untraceable tip?
一些匿名的 不可查的 提醒吗

818
01:11:18,540 --> 01:11:20,100
Here's the deal, Frank.
这是我的条件 弗兰克

819
01:11:20,660 --> 01:11:23,460
You're gonna walk out that front door and give yourself up.
你从前门出来 束手就擒

820
01:11:23,660 --> 01:11:25,820
You have my word no one will shoot you.
我保证没人向你们开枪

821
01:11:26,020 --> 01:11:29,660
I'll personally take you in and you will get to tell your side of the story.
我亲自带你回局里 你跟他们解释你的故事

822
01:11:30,340 --> 01:11:32,500
You got 60 seconds to decide.
你有 60 秒钟考虑

823
01:11:36,660 --> 01:11:37,660
What's it look like?
外边情况如何

824
01:11:37,740 --> 01:11:39,300
There's no clean exit.
没有好突破口

825
01:11:39,900 --> 01:11:41,860
They seem to be coming from everywhere.
他们把这里包围了

826
01:11:48,100 --> 01:11:50,460
If we had a distraction, I could cover you to the woods.
如果情况突变 我会掩护你进树林

827
01:12:03,300 --> 01:12:05,940
Looks like there's not a lot of options, kid.
好像没有更多办法了 孩子

828
01:12:09,020 --> 01:12:14,260
I mean somebody's gonna have to make the hard choice
我的意思是 必须有人做出艰难的决定

829
01:12:14,340 --> 01:12:15,660
if we are gonna get out of here alive.
保证我们能安全从这里撤出去

830
01:12:30,500 --> 01:12:31,860
Been wild.
野性一把

831
01:12:34,420 --> 01:12:36,140
Wild and crazy.
狂野不羁

832
01:12:37,300 --> 01:12:39,700
But I wouldn't want it any other way.
但我也不想以其他方式结束

833
01:12:46,940 --> 01:12:48,340
An honor.
为了荣誉

834
01:12:55,540 --> 01:12:56,860
Good luck.
祝你好运

835
01:13:06,140 --> 01:13:07,540
Tell your men to hold their fire.
告诉你的人停火

836
01:13:08,020 --> 01:13:09,100
I'm coming out.
我这就出去

837
01:13:10,980 --> 01:13:13,540
He's coming out. All units, hold fire.
他要出来了 所有单位注意 停止射击

838
01:13:13,620 --> 01:13:15,620
Repeat, all units, hold fire.
重复 所有单位 停止射击

839
01:13:15,900 --> 01:13:17,060
Roger that.
遵命

840
01:13:22,620 --> 01:13:23,900
Get behind.
躲我后边

841
01:13:25,580 --> 01:13:27,580
Come out now. I've got you covered.
出来吧 我掩护你

842
01:13:44,420 --> 01:13:45,580
Who fired the shot?
谁开的冷枪

843
01:14:11,420 --> 01:14:13,620
Tell me when the boys make cover, we'll move.
看看大家撤出来后 告诉我一声 我们也撤

844
01:14:15,620 --> 01:14:16,660
Now.
现在

845
01:14:53,140 --> 01:14:54,740
They've got Sarah.
他们抓住莎拉了

846
01:14:58,260 --> 01:14:59,900
Frank, you're no good to her dead.
弗兰克 她的死与你无关

847
01:15:00,100 --> 01:15:01,340
We gotta move.
我们必须撤了

848
01:15:06,620 --> 01:15:08,700
Now is not time to waste.
没时间浪费了

849
01:15:09,340 --> 01:15:10,500
Ivan?
伊万

850
01:15:14,220 --> 01:15:16,500
It's nice to see you again, Ivan.
见到你真高兴 伊万

851
01:15:16,580 --> 01:15:17,980
Did he just call you "bunny"?
他刚才叫你 小兔兔

852
01:15:20,740 --> 01:15:22,580
Life sometimes is complicated.
生活总是纷繁复杂的

853
01:15:30,780 --> 01:15:32,100
To Joe.
敬乔

854
01:15:34,460 --> 01:15:35,780
Joe.
敬乔

855
01:15:46,340 --> 01:15:49,460
Not to push the bounds of propriety,
别怪我说话没分寸

856
01:15:49,660 --> 01:15:51,420
but don't you think we ought to discuss the fact that
但大家不该讨论一下这个事实吗

857
01:15:51,500 --> 01:15:55,300
the CIA's being used by the Vice President as his personal hit squad
中情局现在已经是副总统的私人打手

858
01:15:55,380 --> 01:15:58,700
and that they'll do whatever they can to find us and kill us?
他们会竭尽所能找到我们并除掉

859
01:16:00,900 --> 01:16:02,140
Options?
方案吗

860
01:16:04,220 --> 01:16:05,820
We could go public.
我们可以公之与众

861
01:16:06,020 --> 01:16:10,300
Yeah, right. That didn't work very well for the reporter.
说的轻巧 那个记者就是这么死的

862
01:16:10,580 --> 01:16:12,420
And what about Frank's girlfriend?
弗兰克女朋友怎么办

863
01:16:12,740 --> 01:16:14,220
They'll kill her so fast.
他们会马上杀了她

864
01:16:15,020 --> 01:16:18,580
First they'll interrogate her. They probably already got the wires.
他们会先审问她 很可能现在就已经拿着钢丝绳

865
01:16:18,660 --> 01:16:21,900
Then give her a little snorkel. Give her a jump.
给她个小面罩 逼她跳河

866
01:16:22,100 --> 01:16:23,700
Bring in the dent.
满身伤痕

867
01:16:25,420 --> 01:16:28,340
God! You are such an idiot.
天 你真是个蠢货

868
01:16:41,900 --> 01:16:43,220
I want to show you something.
我给你看样东西

869
01:16:51,060 --> 01:16:52,940
This was done to me by the love of my life.
这是我生命中的至爱 留给我的

870
01:16:54,580 --> 01:16:57,060
It seems that what we had was not meant to be.
也许我们所经历的 没有任何意义

871
01:16:58,180 --> 01:17:00,500
But now she sits
但现在 她

872
01:17:01,300 --> 01:17:03,420
outside my house
坐在我屋外

873
01:17:04,900 --> 01:17:06,940
drinking vodka.
喝着伏特加

874
01:17:11,220 --> 01:17:13,580
Three bullets in the chest.
肩膀上 三颗子弹

875
01:17:14,300 --> 01:17:17,180
When I woke alive,
当我醒来的时候

876
01:17:19,140 --> 01:17:21,140
I knew she still loved me.
我懂 她一直爱着我

877
01:17:21,700 --> 01:17:24,260
Or else it would have been the head.
负责的话 早打在脑袋上了

878
01:17:25,500 --> 01:17:28,180
It was big risk for her, of course,
当然 对她而言这很冒险

879
01:17:28,980 --> 01:17:33,420
but one does crazy things for love.
但对爱而言 这很疯狂

880
01:17:36,500 --> 01:17:39,460
Do not fear for your love, my friend.
不要恐惧你内心的爱 我的朋友

881
01:17:40,100 --> 01:17:42,460
With a small dedicated group,
咱们这些个人聚在一起

882
01:17:42,780 --> 01:17:45,460
there is nothing that cannot be accomplished.
没有什么不可能

883
01:17:46,740 --> 01:17:48,060
Let me be blunt.
我把话挑明了吧

884
01:17:48,500 --> 01:17:51,460
Nobody knows you're here. You don't exist.
没人知道你在这里 你根本不存在

885
01:17:52,260 --> 01:17:54,020
And unless you cooperate fully,
除非你完全合作

886
01:17:54,500 --> 01:17:56,460
there's nothing I can't do to you.
否则我们什么都干的出来

887
01:17:56,980 --> 01:17:58,980
-Sir. -Not now.
-长官 -现在没空

888
01:17:59,060 --> 01:18:00,780
Moses is on the phone.
摩西打电话过来

889
01:18:02,900 --> 01:18:04,660
Okay. Trace is running.
好了 开始追踪

890
01:18:10,660 --> 01:18:11,700
Moses.
摩西

891
01:18:12,180 --> 01:18:13,620
Here's the thing, Cooper.
说心里话 库珀

892
01:18:15,060 --> 01:18:18,300
With age comes a certain perspective.
人们慢慢长大有了自己的看法

893
01:18:18,460 --> 01:18:22,900
I'd be a liar if I said there wasn't a time when I was exactly like you.
若说一点都不欣赏你 那是谎话

894
01:18:23,460 --> 01:18:24,780
Blind ambition.
盲目的志向

895
01:18:25,260 --> 01:18:26,460
Misplaced trust.
错误的信任

896
01:18:26,660 --> 01:18:28,420
Why are you telling me this?
你怎么跟我扯这些

897
01:18:29,580 --> 01:18:31,340
It might help me to decide what to do next.
我在决定接下来怎么行动

898
01:18:31,420 --> 01:18:32,500
Just keep it going.
就这样跟他一直聊

899
01:18:32,660 --> 01:18:34,300
Why? What are you thinking about?
为什么 你在考虑什么

900
01:18:34,820 --> 01:18:37,020
Our business is a very hard one.
我们从事的行业很艰辛

901
01:18:37,500 --> 01:18:38,820
But it was never
但一直以来

902
01:18:39,780 --> 01:18:42,060
the killing or the stress,
血腥杀人 随时备战

903
01:18:42,340 --> 01:18:43,980
or the bad pay that bothered me.
糟糕薪水 都从没困扰我

904
01:18:44,180 --> 01:18:46,180
What was it, Frank?
那是什么 弗兰克

905
01:18:46,660 --> 01:18:51,540
It's how anything that you love can be taken away from you.
困扰我的是 我该如何承受 失去我所爱

906
01:18:52,860 --> 01:18:54,660
It taught me never to care.
职业让我 从不在乎什么

907
01:18:55,020 --> 01:18:56,180
Never to invest.
从不专情与谁

908
01:18:57,900 --> 01:18:59,700
Then I met this woman.
后来我遇上这个女人

909
01:19:00,540 --> 01:19:01,860
Sarah.
莎拉

910
01:19:04,220 --> 01:19:05,740
And now you have her.
而你抓了她

911
01:19:06,380 --> 01:19:09,340
Now I can't think of anything more horrible
我实在想不到 能有什么事情让你害怕

912
01:19:09,540 --> 01:19:13,220
than to know that your enemies can hurt someone that you love.
除了告诫你 你的敌人也能伤害你爱的人

913
01:19:13,660 --> 01:19:16,540
The feeling is almost indescribable.
这种感觉无法形容

914
01:19:22,740 --> 01:19:24,180
You still there, Cooper?
还在听吗 库珀

915
01:19:26,140 --> 01:19:27,380
You're at my house.
你在我家

916
01:19:35,900 --> 01:19:37,820
Almost indescribable, isn't it?
无法形容 不是吗

917
01:19:40,740 --> 01:19:41,820
Please.
求你了

918
01:19:43,860 --> 01:19:45,300
Please don't hurt my family.
求你别伤害我家人

919
01:19:46,540 --> 01:19:48,220
If anything happens to Sarah,
如果莎拉少了一根头发

920
01:19:49,380 --> 01:19:51,580
I will rip everything you love out of your life.
我会把你爱的人一个一个干掉

921
01:19:53,100 --> 01:19:54,540
And then I'll kill you.
最后杀了你

922
01:19:56,980 --> 01:19:59,100
I swear to you, I will keep Sarah safe.
我向你发誓 我确保莎拉安全

923
01:19:59,620 --> 01:20:01,260
We don't have much time.
我们没多少时间

924
01:20:01,460 --> 01:20:02,780
Do you understand that?
你明白吗

925
01:20:06,100 --> 01:20:07,460
What are you gonna do, Frank?
你打算干什么 弗兰克

926
01:20:08,260 --> 01:20:10,140
I'm gonna kill the Vice President.
我要去刺杀副总统

927
01:20:10,620 --> 01:20:11,980
What are you gonna do?
你能怎么办

928
01:21:35,460 --> 01:21:36,820
Frank left this for me.
弗兰克给了我这个

929
01:21:38,980 --> 01:21:40,500
Where did he get it from?
他从哪里弄来的

930
01:21:42,060 --> 01:21:45,180
The secure records depository of the CIA.
中情局安全档案管理库

931
01:21:55,860 --> 01:21:57,700
Look, Sarah.
听着 莎拉

932
01:21:59,660 --> 01:22:02,060
I know Frank's been right about a few things.
我知道 有些事情 弗兰克是对的

933
01:22:03,100 --> 01:22:06,260
But he's about to cross a line from which there's no turning back.
但他正在跨过底线 走上一条不归路

934
01:22:07,260 --> 01:22:10,900
Right now, you have an opportunity to help him.
现在 你有机会去救他

935
01:22:12,060 --> 01:22:14,260
You need to tell me everything you know.
你必须告诉我你知道的一切

936
01:22:14,740 --> 01:22:16,740
Because if I can't stop him,
因为 如果我不能阻止他

937
01:22:18,380 --> 01:22:19,660
I'm gonna have to kill him.
就必须杀了他

938
01:22:26,860 --> 01:22:30,540
Do you know who Frank Moses is? I mean, really is?
你知道弗兰克·摩西是谁吗 我是指 真实身份

939
01:22:31,300 --> 01:22:33,260
Do you know what he's done?
你知道他干什么活的吗

940
01:22:39,580 --> 01:22:41,980
You're asking me for help? That is so lame.
你是在求我帮忙 束手无策了啊

941
01:22:44,100 --> 01:22:45,860
He's gonna eat you for lunch.
他会拿你做午餐

942
01:22:53,020 --> 01:22:54,260
She's never gonna trust us.
她不会信任我们的

943
01:22:54,620 --> 01:22:57,260
I can't blame her. The tip off was a trap.
不能怪她 之前的提醒是个圈套

944
01:22:57,460 --> 01:22:59,780
Someone's got us dancing like marionettes.
我们像木偶被人玩的团团转

945
01:23:05,420 --> 01:23:07,580
Just like Moses called it.
就像摩西说的那样

946
01:23:11,580 --> 01:23:13,140
He will take a shot at the V.P.
他要去刺杀副总统

947
01:23:13,900 --> 01:23:15,940
That's a problem for the Secret Service.
那是特勤局的问题

948
01:23:18,620 --> 01:23:20,860
Moses'll take them apart.
摩西会把他们引开的

949
01:23:22,460 --> 01:23:23,620
Plug me into their detail.
把我加进特勤名单

950
01:23:25,420 --> 01:23:26,740
You got it.
好的

951
01:23:27,580 --> 01:23:28,660
What about her?
她怎么办

952
01:23:29,620 --> 01:23:32,940
I'll keep her close. Protected. Off the grid.
我会看好她 保护她 没有问题

953
01:23:40,140 --> 01:23:43,660
I put a few things away.Just in case.
我私藏了一些货  以防万一

954
01:23:43,780 --> 01:23:44,780
Frank.
弗兰克

955
01:23:50,540 --> 01:23:52,260
Swedish K.
瑞典 K

956
01:23:54,180 --> 01:23:56,780
Now that is exciting.
激动人心哪

957
01:23:59,180 --> 01:24:00,300
Explosives?
有炸弹吗

958
01:24:00,780 --> 01:24:01,980
Just past the RPGs.
枪榴弹那边

959
01:24:02,780 --> 01:24:03,820
I love you, man.
爱死你了

960
01:24:04,500 --> 01:24:07,460
-Make yourself at home. -The Vice President's gonna love this.
-随便拿 -副总统要好受一番啦

961
01:24:57,420 --> 01:24:58,460
Thank you.
谢谢你

962
01:25:07,620 --> 01:25:08,740
I'm sorry.
抱歉

963
01:25:14,740 --> 01:25:15,780
Thank you, ma'am.
谢谢合作 夫人

964
01:25:29,260 --> 01:25:31,620
Thank you very much.
非常感谢

965
01:25:39,940 --> 01:25:41,740
Welcome, Ms. Brown.
热烈欢迎 布朗夫人

966
01:25:44,140 --> 01:25:46,380
It's a pleasure to have you at our Victory Fund Gala.
非常感谢您能参加 胜选基金晚宴

967
01:25:46,660 --> 01:25:48,580
Oh, I'm so looking forward to it.
我也迫不及待啊

968
01:25:53,580 --> 01:25:54,940
Raptor is cleared for entry.
猛禽报告入口安全

969
01:25:55,780 --> 01:25:57,460
After you, Mr. Vice President.
你先请 副总统先生

970
01:25:57,660 --> 01:26:02,460
A true war hero, a fabulous friend and a wonderful leader.
一位真正的战争英雄 优秀的朋友 卓绝的领袖

971
01:26:03,020 --> 01:26:06,500
And so it's with great pleasure I introduce to you,
非常荣幸 由我向大家介绍

972
01:26:07,100 --> 01:26:09,260
vice President Robert Stanton.
副总统先生 罗伯特·斯坦顿

973
01:26:17,780 --> 01:26:20,780
Thank you, everybody. Thank you so much for being here.
谢谢 谢谢大家 非常感谢大家能赏光莅临

974
01:26:21,140 --> 01:26:22,460
I'm gonna keep this short and sweet
我会尽量 说的少 说的好

975
01:26:22,540 --> 01:26:24,700
so you'll actually write those checks you've been promising.
这样大家才不会 给我写空头支票

976
01:26:29,100 --> 01:26:31,060
Seriously, though, great to see you all.
说真的 很高兴见到大家

977
01:26:32,820 --> 01:26:34,260
It's the wonderful people here tonight
正是今晚在座的各位伟大的伙伴

978
01:26:34,340 --> 01:26:36,100
that got us into the White House in the first place.
让我们站在白宫的最前端

979
01:26:36,180 --> 01:26:38,380
And I believe it's this wonderful group of people
而我相信 在座伟大的伙伴们

980
01:26:38,500 --> 01:26:41,620
who will keep us there for a long, long time!
会支持我们在那里 很长很长时间

981
01:26:44,020 --> 01:26:45,820
My good friends,
我亲爱的朋友们

982
01:26:46,100 --> 01:26:48,740
I am proud to announce that I will be forming an exploratory committee
我正式宣布 组建一个竞选委员会

983
01:26:48,820 --> 01:26:52,420
with the primary goal of seeking a nomination for the Presidency.
以达成伟大的目标 成功竞选总统

984
01:27:02,220 --> 01:27:05,180
We've had a great journey together.
我们曾携手走过一段伟大的旅程

985
01:27:05,340 --> 01:27:09,380
But I firmly believe that the best is still to come.
我也坚定的相信 最好的即将到来

986
01:27:10,340 --> 01:27:11,740
God bless you all.
上帝保佑你们

987
01:27:12,180 --> 01:27:13,820
God bless America!
上帝保佑美利坚

988
01:27:38,180 --> 01:27:39,540
Hello, bunny.
你好 小兔兔

989
01:27:39,980 --> 01:27:42,140
Moves like that could get you killed.
这样胡闹会让我杀了你

990
01:27:42,820 --> 01:27:46,420
Your radiance tonight renders me almost speechless.
今晚你光彩照人 我几乎说不出话来

991
01:27:46,500 --> 01:27:47,540
Almost.
差点

992
01:27:51,740 --> 01:27:53,100
What are you grinning at?
你笑嘻嘻干啥呢

993
01:27:53,980 --> 01:27:57,260
I've always dreamed of killing an American President.
我一直梦想 能够杀个美国总统玩玩

994
01:27:57,420 --> 01:27:58,580
Vice President.
这是副总统

995
01:27:59,060 --> 01:28:00,060
Whatever.
差不多啦

996
01:28:01,380 --> 01:28:05,260
Having you in my arms once again, I get carried away.
再次把你拥在怀中 我得意忘形啊

997
01:28:05,540 --> 01:28:06,580
Really?
真的吗

998
01:28:09,060 --> 01:28:10,380
Tell me you love me.
告诉我你爱我

999
01:28:12,060 --> 01:28:13,980
It's been a long time, Ivan.
已经很久了 伊万

1000
01:28:14,580 --> 01:28:15,820
Blink of an eye.
就一句嘛

1001
01:28:18,940 --> 01:28:20,500
Ivan.
伊万

1002
01:28:20,580 --> 01:28:22,420
The music has stopped.
音乐已经停了

1003
01:28:23,380 --> 01:28:24,580
Is it?
是吗

1004
01:28:27,940 --> 01:28:29,260
To work then.
该行动了

1005
01:28:35,620 --> 01:28:36,740
Ivan!
伊万

1006
01:28:51,820 --> 01:28:53,140
Do you smell that?
你闻到了吗

1007
01:29:15,900 --> 01:29:18,100
-This area is off limits. -No, it's fine. It's fine.
-本区域禁行  -没关系 没关系

1008
01:29:18,300 --> 01:29:19,420
You'll have to turn around.
请您回去

1009
01:29:19,580 --> 01:29:21,140
No, it's fine.
哦 没关系

1010
01:29:21,620 --> 01:29:23,340
It's all right. I'm sure I'm allowed.
没关系 我确信我有权过来

1011
01:29:23,420 --> 01:29:26,540
You'll have to go back up, ma'am, or I'll have to treat you as a threat.
您必须立刻回去 夫人 否则我们会视同威胁

1012
01:29:26,620 --> 01:29:27,980
Where exactly is the threat?
威胁究竟在哪儿

1013
01:29:51,020 --> 01:29:53,500
Gas! I smell gas!
煤气 有煤气

1014
01:29:53,580 --> 01:29:55,980
Gas! Gas!
煤气 煤气

1015
01:29:56,340 --> 01:29:57,380
Gas!
煤气

1016
01:30:07,340 --> 01:30:08,580
Stand aside.
靠边站

1017
01:30:11,380 --> 01:30:13,340
Primary exit blocked. Secondary, move.
常规出口封闭 备用通道 快

1018
01:30:13,420 --> 01:30:15,020
Move! Move! Move!
快 快 快

1019
01:31:08,100 --> 01:31:09,420
What the hell are they using?
他们用的什么鬼东西

1020
01:31:30,740 --> 01:31:33,100
Get back up in here to the north stairwell, now!
步行梯北 需要支援 快

1021
01:32:03,700 --> 01:32:05,460
Move to the other limo. I'll cover you.
快换另一辆车 我掩护你

1022
01:32:26,740 --> 01:32:29,100
We have to go. Now! Now!
我们必须撤退啦 快 快

1023
01:32:36,140 --> 01:32:37,660
Approaching target from the rear.
从后面接近目标

1024
01:33:03,380 --> 01:33:04,620
Outside!
外边

1025
01:33:05,700 --> 01:33:07,140
Secret Service, everybody down!
特勤局 大家都趴下

1026
01:33:32,020 --> 01:33:33,140
Cover us! We're moving now!
掩护我们 现在就行动

1027
01:33:35,260 --> 01:33:36,900
Come on! Move!
加把劲 快

1028
01:33:43,500 --> 01:33:46,260
I remember the Secret Service being tougher.
我记得特勤局通常很牛逼的

1029
01:33:46,340 --> 01:33:47,500
Me, too.
我更牛

1030
01:34:00,220 --> 01:34:01,420
Marvin.
马文

1031
01:34:04,500 --> 01:34:05,780
Bugger!
妈的

1032
01:34:36,220 --> 01:34:37,620
-Almost there. -Marvin.
-快到了 -马文

1033
01:34:37,900 --> 01:34:38,980
We gotta move.
我们得离开了

1034
01:34:39,580 --> 01:34:43,100
You're on your own. I'm no use anymore.
你自己走 我不能拖你后腿

1035
01:34:44,580 --> 01:34:46,580
Good luck. Go on.
保重 走吧

1036
01:34:50,860 --> 01:34:52,500
Let's move!
我们走

1037
01:34:54,180 --> 01:34:55,540
Are you hit, sir?
你受伤了吗 长官

1038
01:34:55,900 --> 01:34:58,100
-Are you hit? -I'm fine! Just get me the hell out of here.
-你受伤吗 -我很好 快点我把弄出这鬼地方

1039
01:35:16,980 --> 01:35:20,540
Perhaps I could be of assistance?
也许 我能帮上忙

1040
01:35:34,460 --> 01:35:35,780
I love you.
我爱你

1041
01:35:36,140 --> 01:35:37,380
I know.
我知道

1042
01:35:44,820 --> 01:35:45,900
Freeze!
站住

1043
01:35:57,300 --> 01:35:58,540
Go. Go!
快跑

1044
01:36:00,820 --> 01:36:01,900
Go!
快

1045
01:36:12,660 --> 01:36:15,140
Get in! Get in!
进去 进去

1046
01:36:15,860 --> 01:36:16,940
Go, go, go!
快开 快

1047
01:36:21,300 --> 01:36:23,700
Stop the car! Stop...
停车 停车

1048
01:36:23,780 --> 01:36:25,420
Don't you dare stop! You keep going!
不准停 快开车

1049
01:36:25,500 --> 01:36:27,500
Stop the car! Pull over!
停车 靠边停车

1050
01:36:35,900 --> 01:36:37,860
I wanna know what the hell that was all about!
我要查清 这一切究竟是他妈怎么回事

1051
01:36:58,260 --> 01:37:00,260
Get him off!
把他摔下去

1052
01:37:00,540 --> 01:37:02,060
Pull over!
靠边停车

1053
01:37:03,780 --> 01:37:05,620
Raptor is secure.
猛禽安全

1054
01:37:22,500 --> 01:37:23,700
Who are you?
你是谁

1055
01:37:23,940 --> 01:37:25,740
One of the men you ordered killed.
一个你准备除掉的人

1056
01:37:27,340 --> 01:37:29,540
I don't know what you're talking about.
我不知道你在说些什么

1057
01:37:29,940 --> 01:37:31,460
Guatemala.
危地马拉

1058
01:37:32,900 --> 01:37:34,180
I was there.
我参与了

1059
01:37:47,700 --> 01:37:50,140
I'm sure we can negotiate something.
我觉得 我们应该谈谈

1060
01:37:50,580 --> 01:37:52,380
Starting to come back to you now, is it?
开始露出本身熊样了 啊

1061
01:37:54,380 --> 01:37:56,380
If you're looking for revenge...
如果你要复仇

1062
01:37:56,700 --> 01:37:58,620
This is not about revenge.
这与复仇无关

1063
01:38:03,820 --> 01:38:05,740
Are you gonna kill me?
你会杀了我吗

1064
01:38:08,340 --> 01:38:09,620
Not just you.
不止你

1065
01:38:22,100 --> 01:38:24,140
I'm at the Evanston power plant.
我在<i>埃文斯顿</i> 发电厂

1066
01:38:24,620 --> 01:38:26,780
You have 15 minutes to bring me Sarah.
你有 15 分钟把莎拉带过来

1067
01:38:26,900 --> 01:38:29,100
Or I kill the vice President.
不然我就杀了副总统

1068
01:38:33,420 --> 01:38:35,340
He just made contact. He wants the girl.
摩西带电话来了 他要那姑娘

1069
01:38:35,420 --> 01:38:38,180
Evanston Power Station. 15 minutes.
<i>埃文斯顿</i> 发电厂 15 分钟

1070
01:38:38,780 --> 01:38:40,340
You better alert Secret Service.
你最好通知特勤局

1071
01:38:40,540 --> 01:38:41,660
Copy that.
收到

1072
01:38:42,620 --> 01:38:44,780
Secret Service is en route.
特勤局 已上路

1073
01:39:07,980 --> 01:39:09,300
Where's Sarah?
莎拉呢

1074
01:39:09,660 --> 01:39:11,020
She's on her way.
路上呢

1075
01:39:13,220 --> 01:39:14,900
It's over, Frank.
结束了 弗兰克

1076
01:39:15,540 --> 01:39:17,860
Any minute the whole world is gonna drop on you.
每一分钟 这个世界都在抛弃你

1077
01:39:18,940 --> 01:39:20,300
We'll see.
走着瞧

1078
01:39:44,100 --> 01:39:46,580
Hey, tough guy.
嘿 壮汉

1079
01:39:48,140 --> 01:39:49,660
Surprised to see me?
见到我很惊讶吧

1080
01:39:51,300 --> 01:39:52,380
What the hell's this?
这究竟怎么回事

1081
01:39:52,500 --> 01:39:53,540
Alex...
艾利克斯

1082
01:39:54,140 --> 01:39:57,740
Just give him what he wants. I can't do this anymore.
他要什么都给他 我再也不干了

1083
01:40:00,860 --> 01:40:02,900
You ordered these killings, not me.
你下的追杀令 不是我

1084
01:40:04,260 --> 01:40:06,540
I don't want to have anything to do with this anymore.
我再也 不想跟这破事 有任何干系啦

1085
01:40:12,300 --> 01:40:13,740
You shot me.
你打我

1086
01:40:14,740 --> 01:40:16,180
Shut up.
闭嘴

1087
01:40:20,260 --> 01:40:23,100
I loved watching you being a good guy.
我喜欢看你演好人

1088
01:40:24,340 --> 01:40:27,100
Kicking ass for your country.
为你的国家 奔走效命

1089
01:40:28,380 --> 01:40:31,340
It showed a spectacular lack of vision.
你真是缺乏远见 蠢到家了

1090
01:40:32,620 --> 01:40:33,780
The girl goes free.
把女孩儿放了

1091
01:40:34,620 --> 01:40:36,140
That'll cost you a gun.
那你得挨一枪

1092
01:40:41,420 --> 01:40:43,100
A life for a life.
一命换一命

1093
01:40:47,380 --> 01:40:49,460
I tore up all those checks.
我把养老支票都撕了

1094
01:40:50,660 --> 01:40:52,100
I know.
我知道

1095
01:40:55,460 --> 01:40:56,980
I just wanted to talk to you.
我只想过跟你说会儿话

1096
01:41:04,140 --> 01:41:05,140
Cooper
库珀

1097
01:41:06,300 --> 01:41:07,460
cuff him.
把他铐上

1098
01:41:20,820 --> 01:41:22,900
Wilkes told me you had promise.
威尔克斯 说你发过誓

1099
01:41:22,980 --> 01:41:25,300
Okay, here's how it goes.
好吧 事情这么办

1100
01:41:25,500 --> 01:41:27,980
Moses just shot the V.P.
摩西要枪杀副总统

1101
01:41:28,300 --> 01:41:30,420
You kill him and the girl,
你击毙了摩西和女孩儿

1102
01:41:30,620 --> 01:41:33,180
and you're head of the CIA.
然后你做中情局的头儿

1103
01:41:35,020 --> 01:41:36,100
Cooper.
库珀

1104
01:41:38,580 --> 01:41:40,380
This is gonna happen either way.
不管怎样都会这样的

1105
01:41:42,940 --> 01:41:44,340
Fuck you, Cynthia.
去死吧 辛迪娅

1106
01:42:42,220 --> 01:42:43,580
Thanks.
谢谢你

1107
01:42:48,580 --> 01:42:49,900
This gonna be a problem?
他会出什么差错吗

1108
01:42:53,820 --> 01:42:55,020
No.
不会

1109
01:42:56,100 --> 01:42:57,180
I got it...
我能搞定

1110
01:42:58,740 --> 01:43:00,020
Grandpa.
老头子

1111
01:43:11,340 --> 01:43:12,420
Feel better now?
爽了吗

1112
01:43:12,740 --> 01:43:13,780
Yeah.
爽死了

1113
01:43:14,420 --> 01:43:16,220
Wanna get pancakes?
想吃甜饼吗

1114
01:43:19,300 --> 01:43:21,980
Can you believe it? It all worked out.
你相信吗 梦想成真啦

1115
01:43:22,220 --> 01:43:25,660
Something bad is gonna happen very soon.
坏事情马上会发生

1116
01:43:26,340 --> 01:43:28,500
Maybe not. Wait a second.
也许不会 等一下

1117
01:43:29,540 --> 01:43:30,900
Nobody's chasing us.
没人追我们了

1118
01:43:32,260 --> 01:43:34,340
No one's trying to kill us.
没人要杀我们

1119
01:43:35,300 --> 01:43:37,820
I think we just got our lives back.
我想我们又恢复常态了

1120
01:43:38,780 --> 01:43:40,100
Almost.
差点

1121
01:43:41,500 --> 01:43:43,740
You still owe me a small favor.
你还得替我干一件小事

1122
01:43:46,140 --> 01:43:47,620
His timing is terrible.
真不会挑时候

1123
01:43:48,100 --> 01:43:50,220
You gave a favor to him?
